The evidence with the title 'Scam alert: Delta Airlines is not giving away tickets | WREG.com ' says Jul 11, 2017  ... The Facebook scam claims Delta Airlines is giving away free tickets and  ... Sharing it and completing surveys , by claiming that they have to do so in order for a chance of receiving one of the free airline tickets .  ... Once they get so many people to visit their site , they turn around and sell it to the highest bidder . 
